---
import PageShell from '../../components/PageShell.astro';
import CTABox from '../../components/CTABox.astro';
import ComparisonTable from '../../components/ComparisonTable.astro';

const tocItems = [
  { id: 'overview', text: 'Overview', level: 2 },
  { id: 'coverage-comparison', text: 'Coverage Comparison', level: 2 },
  { id: 'pricing', text: 'Pricing', level: 2 },
  { id: 'network-and-claims', text: 'Network and Claims', level: 2 },
  { id: 'who-should-choose', text: 'Who Should Choose Which', level: 2 },
  { id: 'verdict', text: 'Our Verdict', level: 2 },
];

const relatedLinks = [
  { title: 'Aetna International Review', href: '/providers/aetna-international' },
  { title: 'AXA Global Review', href: '/providers/axa-global' },
  { title: 'Best Expat Insurance', href: '/best/expat-health-insurance' },
];

const coverageColumns = [
  { key: 'feature', header: 'Feature' },
  { key: 'aetna', header: 'Aetna International' },
  { key: 'axa', header: 'AXA Global' },
];

const coverageRows = [
  { feature: 'Inpatient Care', aetna: true, axa: true },
  { feature: 'Outpatient Care', aetna: true, axa: true },
  { feature: 'Mental Health', aetna: 'Moderate', axa: 'Limited' },
  { feature: 'Maternity', aetna: '10-12 mo wait', axa: '10-12 mo wait' },
  { feature: 'Dental', aetna: 'Optional', axa: 'Optional' },
  { feature: 'Telemedicine', aetna: true, axa: true },
  { feature: 'Medical Evacuation', aetna: true, axa: true },
  { feature: 'US Coverage', aetna: 'Included (most plans)', axa: 'Add-on' },
  { feature: 'Prescription Benefits', aetna: 'CVS integration', axa: 'Standard' },
];

const pricingColumns = [
  { key: 'age', header: 'Age' },
  { key: 'aetna', header: 'Aetna International' },
  { key: 'axa', header: 'AXA Global' },
];

const pricingRows = [
  { age: '30', aetna: '$160-250/mo', axa: '$140-220/mo' },
  { age: '40', aetna: '$220-340/mo', axa: '$190-300/mo' },
  { age: '50', aetna: '$290-440/mo', axa: '$260-400/mo' },
  { age: '60', aetna: '$420-640/mo', axa: '$380-580/mo' },
];
---

<PageShell
  title="Aetna International vs AXA Global"
  description="Compare Aetna International and AXA Global health insurance. US-backed with CVS benefits vs European global insurer."
  headline="Aetna International vs AXA Global"
  subheadline="US healthcare integration vs European insurance tradition. Different strengths for different expats."
  tocItems={tocItems}
  relatedLinks={relatedLinks}
  ctaButtonText="Get Quotes from Both"
  ctaButtonHref="/best/expat-health-insurance"
>
  <h2 id="overview">Overview</h2>
  <p>
    Aetna International (CVS Health) and AXA Global represent American and European approaches to international health insurance. Aetna excels at US integration; AXA offers global reach with European roots.
  </p>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Aetna International</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-600">
        <li>CVS Health backing</li>
        <li>US coverage included by default</li>
        <li>CVS prescription integration</li>
        <li>Better mental health coverage</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">AXA Global</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-600">
        <li>French-headquartered global giant</li>
        <li>Competitive pricing (excl. US)</li>
        <li>Strong European networks</li>
        <li>Modular plan structure</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <CTABox
    title="Compare Both Providers"
    description="Get personalized quotes from Aetna and AXA."
    buttonText="Get Free Quotes"
    buttonHref="/best/expat-health-insurance"
    variant="highlight"
  />

  <h2 id="coverage-comparison">Coverage Comparison</h2>
  <p>
    Both provide comprehensive international coverage. The key differences are US integration and prescription benefits.
  </p>

  <div class="my-8 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
    <ComparisonTable columns={coverageColumns} rows={coverageRows} />
  </div>

  <p><strong>Key differences:</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li>Aetna includes US coverage; AXA charges 30-40% extra</li>
    <li>Aetna has CVS prescription benefits in the US</li>
    <li>Aetna has better mental health coverage</li>
    <li>AXA has stronger European hospital networks</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="pricing">Pricing</h2>
  <p>
    AXA appears cheaper, but that's without US coverage. Once you add US coverage to AXA, Aetna becomes competitive or cheaper.
  </p>

  <div class="my-8 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
    <ComparisonTable columns={pricingColumns} rows={pricingRows} />
  </div>

  <p><strong>Pricing notes:</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li>Aetna prices include US coverage</li>
    <li>AXA prices exclude US; add 30-40% for inclusion</li>
    <li>For US expats, Aetna often provides better value</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="network-and-claims">Network and Claims</h2>

  <h3>Provider Networks</h3>
  <p>
    <strong>Aetna International</strong> has excellent US coverage through CVS Health plus solid international networks, especially in the Americas.
  </p>
  <p>
    <strong>AXA Global</strong> has strong networks in Europe, Middle East, and Asia-Pacific, reflecting its global footprint.
  </p>

  <h3>Prescription Benefits</h3>
  <p>
    Aetna's CVS integration provides real value for Americans—competitive pricing and convenient access at US pharmacies. AXA offers standard prescription coverage.
  </p>

  <h2 id="who-should-choose">Who Should Choose Which</h2>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
    <div class="bg-primary-50 border border-primary-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Choose Aetna International If:</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-600">
        <li>You're American or need US coverage</li>
        <li>You want CVS prescription benefits</li>
        <li>Mental health coverage matters</li>
        <li>You visit the US regularly</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Choose AXA Global If:</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-600">
        <li>You don't need US coverage</li>
        <li>You're based in Europe</li>
        <li>You prefer European service approach</li>
        <li>Budget without US is priority</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 id="verdict">Our Verdict</h2>
  <p>
    For Americans or anyone needing integrated US healthcare, Aetna International delivers better value. The CVS prescription benefits alone can justify the choice.
  </p>
  <p>
    For Europeans or expats who don't need US coverage, AXA Global offers solid coverage at competitive prices with the backing of one of the world's largest insurers.
  </p>

  <CTABox
    title="Ready to Decide?"
    description="Get quotes from both providers."
    buttonText="Compare Plans Now"
    buttonHref="/best/expat-health-insurance"
    variant="highlight"
  />

  <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6 mt-8">
    <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">
      <strong>Disclaimer:</strong> Prices and coverage details change. Verify all information with providers before purchasing.
    </p>
  </div>
</PageShell>
